                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I can also confirm that AE Pacificy (Wake of Tranquility) will set off traps on chests as well.  While trying to use WoT to single pull our assassination target, I managed to hit a chest that was too close.
<br />
thank goodness the cleric had remove curse.
<br />

<br />
When in doubt, use the single target version if possible.  If I had known about the AE effect setting off traps ahead of time, I could have used pacification instead.
<br />

<br />
At least nobody died, and we still managed to single pull after the curses were removed.
